{"tid":1652953,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港真係越來越似烏克蘭","createTime":"2019-10-14T01:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T15:57:04.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"acc8a0db85fa4311f645abb08364bc6f6396a398","tid":1652953,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:16:37.000Z","msg":"歷史上，烏克蘭成為無數戰爭、移民和文化影響的匯聚之地。而今，處於大國夾縫之中的烏克蘭仍無法抽離歷史的經緯和現實的復雜。<br />\n<br />\n2013年11月23日，<strong>因烏克蘭政府暫停「入歐」進程而引發的示威抗議風潮，最終演變為暴力沖突</strong>、政權更迭、大國介入，從基輔到克里米亞、再到烏東部局勢升級，烏克蘭危機牽動國際社會神經，而由此引發的烏克蘭深層次的政治、經濟、社會危機，以及國際關系（特別是大國關系）的震盪更是「步步驚心」。「新冷戰」的驚呼振聾發聵。烏克蘭危機的影響將極為深遠。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.books.com.tw/products/CN11184506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fproducts%2FCN11184506&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeN%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=084fe1bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.books.com.tw/products/CN11184506</a><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭親歐盟示威<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B9%8C%E5%85%8B%E5%85%B0%E4%BA%B2%E6%AC%A7%E7%9B%9F%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25B9%258C%25E5%2585%258B%25E5%2585%25B0%25E4%25BA%25B2%25E6%25AC%25A7%25E7%259B%259F%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%25BF%2590%25E5%258A%25A8&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeN%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=f6f31590\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B9%8C%E5%85%8B%E5%85%B0%E4%BA%B2%E6%AC%A7%E7%9B%9F%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8</a><br />\n<br />\n抗俄入歐兩頭空&hellip;今昔落差 讓烏克蘭好悶<br />\n<a href=\"https://theme.udn.com/theme/story/6775/3732138https://theme.udn.com/theme/story/6775/3732138\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheme.udn.com%2Ftheme%2Fstory%2F6775%2F3732138https%3A%2F%2Ftheme.udn.com%2Ftheme%2Fstory%2F6775%2F3732138&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeN%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=3d992171\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theme.udn.com/